  "description": {
    "zh": "听着，年轻人，我需要你帮个忙。最近，当我从一次狩猎旅行回到营地时，遇到了一群人，他们需要帮助。他们向我讲述了他们的故事，于是我问他为什么还留在塔科夫——这里对他们来说并不安全。他们既不是士兵，也不是 Scav，更不是为了商业目的而来。我不知道为什么，但他们在疏散后选择留在这里，并一直生存到现在，以为这一切不会持续太久。然而，现实就是如此。他们告诉我，他们已经饿了好几天了，所以我不得不给他们提供食物。我知道该联系谁把他们带出这个区域，所以你不用担心这一点，我可以处理好。现在的问题是，我的食物储备有点短缺，毕竟我的储备并不是为了养活一群饥饿的人准备的。你能帮我筹集一些食物吗？这对我帮助很大。",
    "en": "Listen young one, I need a favor. Recently a bunch of people stumbled upon me when I came back to my camp from a hunting trip, they were looking for help. They told me their story so I asked them why they are still here in Tarkov, they do not belong here, it's not safe for them, they are neither soldiers, bandits or here for business. I don't know why but they chose to stay in Tarkov after evacuation, managed to survive until today, thought that all of this would'nt take too long. Well... here we are. I was told that they were starving for days already so I had to feed them. I might know who to contact to get them out of the zone so that doesn't need to be your concern, I can handle that already. The thing I need from you now is that my food supply got kinda short, after all my supply is not meant for a group of starving guys. Can you organize that for me? This would help me out a lot."
  },
